<mayoclinic:mcimg16x9>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2026/03/Soccer-female-GettyImages-1095259340-.jpg</mayoclinic:mcimg16x9>
