					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->DEAR MAYO CLINIC:&nbsp;For the past several years, I've been competing in half-marathons. This year, I've decided to challenge myself and enter full marathons. What recommendations do you have for preventing sports injuries as I go to this next level? ANSWER:&nbsp;Congratulations on continuing to stretch your goals — and for thinking about preventing injury before you […]<p></p>
