		<title>Mayo Clinic research may bring change to women’s wrestling policies</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-research-may-bring-change-to-womens-wrestling-policies/
		
		<dc:creator><!--[CDATA[Katie Helwig]]--></dc:creator>
